1. *Uveče* sam obično u krevetu oko deset časova. (I usually go to bed around ten o'clock in the evening.)

2. Počinjemo da se spremamo za izlazak *uveče*. (We start to get ready to go out in the evening.)

3. *Uveče* nikad ne jedem prejako. (I never eat too much in the evening.)

4. Imamo običaj da se igramo igrice *uveče*. (We have a custom of playing games in the evening.)

5. *Uveče* nam je mati dolazila da nam čita priče. (Our mother used to come in the evening to read us stories.)